{
  "id": "adv_group_sun_03_05",
  "title": "サニーピース 03 05",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "オーディションの後……\n{user}さんから電話がかかってきた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After the audition…\n{user}-san called me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロで新しくアイドルユニットを作るから……\n参加してみないかって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He said he's forming a new idol unit at Hoshimi Pro…\nand asked if I wanted to join…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.2333329837,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.446462218
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "オーディションは不合格だったけど……私には\nアイドルとして光るものがあるって、言ってくれて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though I failed the audition… he said I have\nwhat it takes to be an idol…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.266666317,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.1487073421
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "それで雫ちゃんは星見プロに入って\nアイドルになったのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you joined Hoshimi Pro\nand became an idol?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.9868038495
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "なってない……その誘いは断った……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No… I turned down the offer…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.9868038495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.9778637567
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "断っちゃったの！？　どうして？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You turned it down?! Why?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.9778637567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.9855969904
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "私はアイドルじゃなくて……マネージャー志望……\n光るものなんてない……私はアイドルに向いてない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to be a manager‚ not an idol…\nI don't have what it takes… I'm not suited to be an idol…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.6458268483,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.7570483523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんにそう言ったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You told {user}-san that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.7570483523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.8570483523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "うん……そうしたら、直接会って\n話がしたいって言われて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… and then he said he wanted to meet\nme in person to talk…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.912493515,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4114.804156399998,
          "startTime": 48.0272976714
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_lesson-00-000-noon",
      "startTime": 47.4606310048
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "兵藤さん、今日は来てくれてありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hyodo-san‚ thank you for coming today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.2272970357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "話があるって言われて、来たけど……\nここ……ダンススタジオ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You said you wanted to talk to me‚ so I came…\nBut this is… a dance studio…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.4458268483,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "実は、兵藤さんに見てほしい人がいるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ there's someone I want you to see‚ Hyodo-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.1048486072,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "彼女は……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who is she…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.371517817,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロからデビュー予定のアイドルの卵だ\n兵藤さんから見て、彼女はどう見える？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She's a trainee who's scheduled to debut from Hoshimi Pro.\nWhat do you think of her‚ Hyodo-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.2880737701,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "……実力不足……ダンスがぎこちなくて\n踊り慣れてないのが一目で分かる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…She's lacking… Her dancing is awkward‚\nand you can tell at a glance that she's not used to dancing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.0124991099,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "でも、慣れないダンスで大変なはずなのに……\n生き生きして、とても楽しそう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But even though she must be struggling with the unfamiliar dance moves…\nshe looks so lively and happy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.3458324432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "笑顔が眩しくて、キラキラ輝いてて……目が離せない\n彼女……アイドルの素質、あると思う……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Her smile is dazzling‚ she's shining brightly… I can't take my eyes off her.\nShe… I think she has the potential to be an idol…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.2458324432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "だが、彼女はアイドルのことを何も知らない\n今のままではアイドルとして生き残れないだろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But she doesn't know anything about being an idol.\nShe won't survive as an idol if she stays like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.8740811585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "他にも、自分に自信がなくて前に進めない子や\n長い間努力しているが日の目を浴びない人……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are other girls who lack confidence and can't move forward‚\nand those who have been working hard for a long time‚ but haven't gotten their chance to shine…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.4407478252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "素質はあるのに一人では輝けない……そういう子達を\n集めて、新しいグループを作りたいと思っている",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They have the potential‚ but can't shine on their own…\nI want to gather those girls and create a new group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.3407478252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "一人では輝けない子が、仲間と一緒に輝くグループ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A group where girls who can't shine alone can shine together with their comrades…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.1407468079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "何も知らない子と、知っているが故に前に進めない子が\n手を組んで、一歩一歩進んでいくんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The girls who know nothing‚ and the girls who can't move forward because they know too much‚\nwill join hands and take one step at a time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.3885308026,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "兵藤さん。星見プロで、同じ夢を目指す仲間と一緒に\nアイドルをやってみないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hyodo-san‚ would you like to be an idol at Hoshimi Pro‚\ntogether with comrades who share the same dream?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.6218539634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "でも……私はアイドルに向いてない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… I'm not suited to be an idol…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.5885196128,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "兵藤さんはアイドルに向いてるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're suited to be an idol‚ Hyodo-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.1350049255,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "こんなにアイドルを好きな子が\nアイドルに向いてないはずないだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Someone who loves idols this much\ncan't possibly be unsuited to be one.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.6350059428,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "誰よりもファンの気持ちが分かる君なら\n誰よりもファンを大切にする素敵なアイドルになれる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You‚ who understands the feelings of the fans better than anyone else‚\ncan become a wonderful idol who cherishes the fans more than anyone else.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.0016726094,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
