      "text": "（お姉ちゃんの他にも）\n（私がアイドルに向いてるって信じてる人がいる……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Besides my sister‚）\n（there's someone else who believes I'm cut out to be an idol…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.4791606902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
