      "text": "（本当は……お姉ちゃんのライブを初めて観た時から）\n（ずっと憧れてた……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Actually… ever since I saw my sister's live for the first time‚）\n（I've always admired it…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.0791545866,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
