      "text": "（ファンの声援を受けて……ペンライトの光の海を見て）\n（笑顔になれたらって、ずっと思ってた……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I've always wanted to be able to）\n（smile while being showered with the fans' cheers and bathed in the sea of penlights…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.1458243051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-szk017.m4a",
      "text": "（私には無理なんだって諦めてたけど……）\n（この人を信じてついて行けば……ひょっとしたら……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I gave up‚ thinking it was impossible for me…）\n（But if I trust this person and follow him… maybe…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.1791576384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
