      "text": "私……喋るのが苦手で……人と関わることも下手で……\n上手に笑うことも出来ないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I… I'm not good at talking… and I'm bad at socializing…\nI can't even smile properly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.8458192187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
