      "text": "それでも……そんな私だけど……アイドルになりたい\nずっと見上げてたステージに、私も立ちたい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But even so… even if I'm like that… I want to be an idol.\nI want to stand on that stage I've always been looking up at…",
        "id": ""
