    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "秋宮もね",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……そっか。雫にもそういうことを話せる友達が",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I see. You made friends you can talk to about that kind of thing‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 352.5687189971,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "秋宮もね",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "出来たんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 357.9999898274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-szk030.m4a",
      "text": "うん……。話してる内にいろんなことを思い出して……\nこの想いを、お姉ちゃんに伝えなきゃって思った……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… While we were talking‚ I remembered a lot of things…\nAnd I thought I had to tell you how I feel…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 365.5212671436,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-szk031.m4a",
      "text": "さっきはいきなりで、びっくりして……\nちゃんと言えなかったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was so surprised earlier…\nI couldn't say it properly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 372.7212671436,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-szk032.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃん、長い間お疲れ様……\n今までありがとう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Onee-chan‚ you've worked hard for so long…\nThank you for everything…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 379.9212610401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_05-szk033.m4a",
      "text": "これからは私が、お姉ちゃんの分まで頑張る……\nアイドルの頂点を目指す……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From now on‚ I'll work hard‚ for you too…\nI'll aim for the top of the idol world…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 386.5212610401,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "秋宮もね",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うん……。雫の口から、その言葉を聞けて嬉しいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… I'm happy to hear you say that‚ Shizuku.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 389.1106005265,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "秋宮もね",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今度は私が、客席から雫を応援するね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now it's my turn to cheer for you from the audience.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 395.4772600724,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
