      "text": "（いつかは私も、アイドルを引退する時が……）\n（来るのかな……今はまだ、考えられないけど……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Will there be a time… when I retire from being an idol too…?）\n（I can't imagine it now‚ but…）",
